item.title: By: susankay500
item.dc:creator: susankay500
item.description:
It's great to see the noble tradition of Weird Bird Friday spreading throughout the land, Doug! I'll take your imitation as flattery and say, "Thanks!"
Great elk picture. Are they really smelly? I don't think I've ever been close enough to one to notice.
item.content:encoded:
It’s great to see the noble tradition of Weird Bird Friday spreading throughout the land, Doug! I’ll take your imitation as flattery and say, “Thanks!”

Great elk picture. Are they really smelly? I don’t think I’ve ever been close enough to one to notice.
